name: "Stranger" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] He comes to you in your dreams and whispers odd stories of floating cars, meals in pill form, and teleportation. He is a stranger from an alternate timeline in which we all still believe that the future will be BETTER than the present. Then, the nightmare happens. You awake to find that you're still living in THIS reality and not the Stranger's... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
